          "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An intruder enters the belfry (D15).</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The bell rises amid shrieking spirits and rings twice. <strong>First peal:</strong> every denizen of Scarwall is alerted — the castle's inhabitants gain a <strong>+10 bonus to Perception for 24 hours</strong>. <strong>Second peal</strong>, focused on the intruders: @Damage[10d6[sonic]] to all creatures in D15 and permanent deafness; @Check[type:fortitude|dc:22] negates the deafness and halves the damage.</p>"
